      <t>This document proposes guidelines for the design of Autonomic Service Agents for autonomic networks.  Autonomic Service Agents, together with the Autonomic Network Infrastructure, the Autonomic Control Plane, and the GeneRic Autonomic Signaling Protocol, constitute base elements of an autonomic networking ecosystem.
